{"tid":98100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那團大跌僅幾十團 北京客：香港空氣比北京好","createTime":"2017-01-28T07:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T01:54:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc7959b86c2b716d74963055c11e7d0f17735b3","tid":98100,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170128/large/1485584655_bf7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170128%2Flarge%2F1485584655_bf7d.jpg&h=f03da168&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大年初一，有財神現身金紫荊廣場，向旅客派發金色朱古力，不少旅客都面露歡顏，紛紛上前合照，希望在新年沾上財氣。現場所見旅客較為疏落，有北京旅客表示，很喜歡香港，「空氣比北京好」。 <br />\n<br />\n旅遊促進會總幹事崔定邦表示，雞年中國訪港旅客數字並不理想，整體數字很少，今日大年初一只得數十團，「比起過往二百團相差好遠」。 <br />\n<br />\n旅促會顧問何鎮東化身財神在金紫荊廣場派發金幣朱古力，他表示活動是為了向旅客宣揚香港好客精神，「我哋係好樂意接待訪港旅客，無論內地或者其他地方。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170128/large/1485584714_2dd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170128%2Flarge%2F1485584714_2dd8.jpg&h=b8e1ba3d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n北京旅客劉小姐幾年前來到香港，今年特意帶母親來港過新年，「希望帶媽媽好好體驗一下」，稍後將會到迪士尼及海洋公園玩，母親劉太太表示，「香港很不錯，空氣比北京好。」 <br />\n<br />\n哈爾濱旅客趙小姐也特意帶家人來港過新年，因為過年「哈爾濱比較冷」，母親趙太太表示，來港旅行是她的「終身夢想，終於看到了」，她覺得香港很繁華，在世界上很出名，因此一直「想看看香港到底是怎麼樣。」婆婆亦大讚香港的景色、環境、空氣，「終究來到了，實現了」，趙小姐稍後將會帶家人到銅鑼灣逛街及搭山頂纜車。"},{"pid":"a6f1fbeca318f48deb5f64ac9af0f8988213e869","tid":98100,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"裝多啲香港山頂空氣返去買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da21b99bf4d111ece201498822fef434783536d5","tid":98100,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>裝多啲香港山頂空氣返去<span style=\"color: red;\">賣</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"afa4b35a980720fa54c6283e3efa70218a7844b8","tid":98100,"uid":14799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>裝多啲香港山頂空氣返去<span style=\"color: red;\">賣</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n香港山頂肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee917277b132cd3e0c8260e309aa5e4ba399d780","tid":98100,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b79c8c65839a4e511e260bc536b0533092474188","tid":98100,"uid":71728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:31:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港空氣出名差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇強國咁閪 d污染物多到伸手唔見五指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d9905cab0d7f425a899df4e12ed31b7e358e96","tid":98100,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"個財神 派金色朱古力果陣<br />\n<br />\nD大陸人 會唔會以為真係金幣<br />\n<br />\n點知發現原來係朱古力, 跟住去屌鳩個財神??<br />\n<br />\n我覺得以大陸人既性格, 好大機會發生呢D事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46681385426842f5c3ee37d0388320d505d219a0","tid":98100,"uid":28277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"大陸都幾慘，水又唔得，食又危險，水又有毒，都唔知點住人"},{"pid":"129b4b31099af6d058a999b7ede2a2bf4845425b","tid":98100,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸都幾慘，水又唔得，食又危險，水又有毒，都唔知點住人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地慘係一件事, 但唔代表佢地做蝗蟲係無錯<br />\n<br />\n即係好似敘利亞人都好慘, 又打仗, 又有ISIS<br />\n但唔代表佢地去歐洲做難民無錯"},{"pid":"34075bf2e7e3c6c4d59d2c2fd3eda491f736fd53","tid":98100,"uid":46910